{"tid":1163195,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】特朗普：在我任內 中國休想經濟超越美國","createTime":"2019-05-20T09:55:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T09:55:25.000Z","uid":70063,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"52ae2ac17d4292212fd8db9c7332246071a98384","tid":1163195,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普說跟中國打這場貿易戰他「特別高興」，還說在他任內中國別想成為世界頭號超級大國。<br />\n<br />\n「我們會有數以十億美元計的進項，」霍氏新聞頻道的Steve Hilton在採訪中問及他貿易戰終局時，特朗普表示，「中國幹得顯然不會有我們這麼好。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普說，眼下中國經濟並不是很好，可是「我們的經濟一直都非常棒。他們在追趕我們，他們想要超越我們。要是希拉莉當總統，到她任滿時，中國經濟規模恐怕就已經比我們大得多了。看看現在，他們連拉近距離都別想。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普還說，他相信中國希望取代美國成為世界頭號超級大國，可這樣的事「在我這兒不會發生」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190520/59621230?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=messenger&amp;utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F59621230%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dmessenger%26utm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGVFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=0cd19416\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F59621230%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dmessenger%26utm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=1e4c75bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190520/59621230?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=messenger&amp;utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_content=share_link</a>"}]}